headline: Traders Are Fleeing Stocks Feared to Be Under Threat From AI
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Artificial intelligence’s imprint on US financial markets is unmistakable. Nvidia Corp. is the most valuable company in the world at nearly $4.5 trillion. Startups from OpenAI to Anthropic have raised tens of billions of dollars. headline: The Smartest Growth Stock to Buy With $1,000 Right Now
summary: Dividend King Coca-Cola isn't cheap, but it also isn't expensive. Add in an attractive yield and strong results, and you might want to buy it right now.
